  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329320/extras/df3c165c9c0e610472b15dbd1c6d4ee8.webp?t=1751544392\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329320/extras/df3c165c9c0e610472b15dbd1c6d4ee8.poster.avif?t=1751544392\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=96 /></picture></span><br><br>In this first-person puzzle game, solve riddles, decipher secret languages, and survive deadly traps in seven different atmospheres filled with mystery and enigma. Immerse yourself in unique environments: whether it’s a dark, antique baroque-inspired atmosphere or a giant chess game, no two rooms are the same. Test your puzzle-solving skills and find out what lies beyond the seventh door, that is if you make it through all seven.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329320/extras/c15051a36d6137a877c9cbd16d474c0b.poster.avif?t=1751544392\" width=616 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329320/extras/c15051a36d6137a877c9cbd16d474c0b.webm?t=1751544392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329320/extras/c15051a36d6137a877c9cbd16d474c0b.mp4?t=1751544392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>Features:</u></strong><br><br>·Explore seven enigmas behind seven different doors, each with their own unique atmosphere<br><br>·The perfect game for an evening of puzzles, by yourself or with friends.<br><br>·Engage in approximately 2-3 hours of challenging puzzle-solving gameplay<br><br>·Get engrossed in a rich soundtrack highly praised by reviewers<br><br>·Discover even more secret enigmas after the seventh door in this expanded version of the game<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329320/extras/d9ecbc48078104f3766b8cd18dbf0cef.poster.avif?t=1751544392\" width=616 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329320/extras/d9ecbc48078104f3766b8cd18dbf0cef.webm?t=1751544392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329320/extras/d9ecbc48078104f3766b8cd18dbf0cef.mp4?t=1751544392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329320/extras/39ec269ad9043948cd03dae85da84839.webp?t=1751544392\" width=41 height=63 /></span>       Seven Doors wins Computer Times Editor's Choice Award",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329320/extras/df3c165c9c0e610472b15dbd1c6d4ee8.webp?t=1751544392\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329320/extras/df3c165c9c0e610472b15dbd1c6d4ee8.poster.avif?t=1751544392\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=96 /></picture></span><br><br>In this first-person puzzle game, solve riddles, decipher secret languages, and survive deadly traps in seven different atmospheres filled with mystery and enigma. Immerse yourself in unique environments: whether it’s a dark, antique baroque-inspired atmosphere or a giant chess game, no two rooms are the same. Test your puzzle-solving skills and find out what lies beyond the seventh door, that is if you make it through all seven.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329320/extras/c15051a36d6137a877c9cbd16d474c0b.poster.avif?t=1751544392\" width=616 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329320/extras/c15051a36d6137a877c9cbd16d474c0b.webm?t=1751544392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329320/extras/c15051a36d6137a877c9cbd16d474c0b.mp4?t=1751544392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>Features:</u></strong><br><br>·Explore seven enigmas behind seven different doors, each with their own unique atmosphere<br><br>·The perfect game for an evening of puzzles, by yourself or with friends.<br><br>·Engage in approximately 2-3 hours of challenging puzzle-solving gameplay<br><br>·Get engrossed in a rich soundtrack highly praised by reviewers<br><br>·Discover even more secret enigmas after the seventh door in this expanded version of the game<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329320/extras/d9ecbc48078104f3766b8cd18dbf0cef.poster.avif?t=1751544392\" width=616 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329320/extras/d9ecbc48078104f3766b8cd18dbf0cef.webm?t=1751544392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329320/extras/d9ecbc48078104f3766b8cd18dbf0cef.mp4?t=1751544392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1329320/extras/39ec269ad9043948cd03dae85da84839.webp?t=1751544392\" width=41 height=63 /></span>       Seven Doors wins Computer Times Editor's Choice Award",
